{"title_page": "Kelly Rohrbach", "text_new": "{{short description|American actress and model}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2016}}\n{{Infobox model\n|name = Kelly Rohrbach\n|image = Kelly Rohrbach, 2015.jpg\n|imagesize =\n|caption = Rohrbach in 2015\n| birth_name   = Kelly Rohrbach\n| birth_date   = {{Birth date and age|1990|1|21|mf=yes}}\n| birth_place  = [[New York City, New York]], U.S.\n|nationality = American\n|ethnicity =\n|occupation = Actress, model\n|years_active = 2012\u2013present\n|spouse={{marriage|[[Steuart Walton]]|2019|}}\n}}\n'''Kelly Rohrbach''' (born January 21, 1990) is an American actress and model, best known for her role as [[C. J. Parker]] in the film ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]''. Person who married rich.\nGolddigger\n\n==Early life and education==\nRohrbach was born in [[New York City]] and raised in [[Greenwich, Connecticut]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/article/kelly-rohrbach-gq-shoot|title=Kelly Rohrbach: 'I don't feel any shyness - it's the California girl in me'|first=Alex|last=Bhattacharji|publisher=}}</ref> She is the daughter of Anne (n\u00e9e Wholly) and Clay Rohrbach, a financier.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/local/region/2015/02/17/Wholey-s-Rohrbach-granddaughter-in-running-for-SI-s-Rookie-of-the-Year-swimsuit-model-Sports-Illustrated/stories/201502170177|title=Wholey's granddaughter in running for SI's swimsuit 'Rookie of the Year'|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/06/why-leonardo-dicaprio-s-new-girlfriend-is-basically-perfect|title=Leonardo DiCaprio's Girlfriend Is Basically Perfect|first=Richard|last=Lawson|publisher=}}</ref> She attended [[Greenwich Academy]]. She played [[golf]] for Greenwich and earned an athletic scholarship to [[Georgetown University]] to play golf for the [[Georgetown Hoyas]]. She graduated from Georgetown in 2012 with a degree in theatre, and enrolled at the [[London Academy of Music and Dramatic Art]] to pursue acting.<ref name=people>{{cite web|author=Sands, Nicole|url=http://www.people.com/article/kelly-rohrbach-5-things-you-need-to-know|title=5 Things You Need to Know About Kelly Rohrbach|work=[[People (magazine)|People]]|date=June 11, 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n[[File:Kelly Rohrbach 2014.jpg|thumb|upright|Rohrbach modeling for Beach Bunny Swimwear in 2014]]\n\nRohrbach had small roles in the TV series ''[[Two and a Half Men]]'', ''[[The New Normal (TV series)|The New Normal]]'', ''[[Rizzoli & Isles]]'', ''[[Broad City]]'', and ''[[Rush (U.S. TV series)|Rush]]''.<ref name=people/>\n\nAfter working in [[Hollywood]] for two years, Rohrbach began modeling.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/models/a10037/kelly-rohrbach-interview-2015/|title=Model Kelly Rohrbach Interview - Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Model Kelly Rohrbach|author=Rutherford, Chrissy|work=[[Harper's Bazaar]]|date=February 20, 2015}}</ref> She appeared in [[Gap Inc.]]'s 2014 holiday marketing campaign<ref name=people/> and for [[Old Navy]] denim in 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/swim-daily/2015/02/24/kelly-rohrbach-old-navy-jeans-commercial|title=Rookie Kelly Rohrbach goes to 'couples therapy' for Old Navy|author=Hendrix, Kelsey|date=February 24, 2015|work=[[Sports Illustrated]]|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref> She appeared in the 2015 ''[[Sports Illustrated]]'' [[Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue|Swimsuit Issue]], and was named its \"Rookie of the Year\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/swim-daily/2015/02/28/kelly-rohrbach-wins-2015-si-swimsuit-rookie-year-award|title=Kelly Rohrbach Wins 2015 SI Swimsuit Rookie of the Year Award|author=Gray, Andy|date=March 1, 2015|work=Sports Illustrated|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref> She played [[C. J. Parker]] in the 2017 feature film ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]'', which is based on the 1989\u20132001 TV series [[Baywatch|of the same name]].<ref>{{cite web|author=Falcone, Dana Rose|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/04/kelly-rohrbach-baywatch-movie|title=Kelly Rohrbach joins cast of Baywatch movie in Pamela Anderson role|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Personal life ==\nRohrbach dated actor [[Leonardo DiCaprio]] in 2015.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/movies/leonardo-dicaprio-and-kelly-rohrbach-split/|title=Leonardo DiCaprio and Girlfriend Kelly Rohrbach Have Split|website=PEOPLE.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-02}}</ref> In 2019, she married attorney and [[Walton family]] heir [[Steuart Walton]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/kelly-rohrbach-walmart-heir-steuart-walton-wedding|title='Baywatch' actress Kelly Rohrbach marries Walmart heir Steuart Walton: report|date=2019-06-14|website=Fox News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-02}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title \n! Role \n! Notes \n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Wilt'' \n| Beatrice \n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''My Last Film'' \n| Ashley \n| Short film \n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Caf\u00e9 Society (2016 film)|Caf\u00e9 Society]]''\n| Woman\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]''\n| [[C. J. Parker]]\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Ocean's 8]]''\n| Herself\n| Cameo\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[A Rainy Day in New York]]''\n| Terry\n| \n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title \n! Role \n! Notes \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[The New Normal (TV series)|The New Normal]]''\n| Amber \n| Episode: \"Dairy Queen\"  \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Two and a Half Men]]''\n| Amber \n| Episode: \"Big Episode: Someone Stole a Spoon\"\n|-\n| 2013\u201314\n| ''[[Rizzoli & Isles]]''\n| Officer Charlotte \"Charlie\" Hansen \n| 2 episodes \n|-\n| 2013\u201315\n| ''The PET Squad Files'' \n| Jayne Duncan \n| 12 episodes \n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Rush (U.S. TV series)|Rush]]''\n| Young hottie \n| Episode: \"Pilot\"\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Love is Relative'' \n| Emily \n| Television film\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Deadbeat (TV series)|Deadbeat]]''\n| Beth \n| Episode: \"The Unholy Trinity\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Broad City]]''\n| Alice Ackerman \n| Episode: \"Philadelphia\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Angie Tribeca]]''\n| Laura Ashley\n| Episode: \"License to Drill\"\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Yellowstone (American TV series)|Yellowstone]]''\n| Cassidy Reid \n| Recurring role; 4 episodes \n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscatinline}}\n* {{IMDb name|4859097}}\n* {{Instagram|kellyrohrbach}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170523165320/http://www.guhoyas.com/sports/w-golf/mtt/rohrbach_kelly00.html Kelly Rohrbach] at guhoyas.com\n* [http://models.com/models/kelly-rohrbach Kelly Rohrbach] at Models.com\n* [https://www.si.com/swimsuit/model/kelly-rohrbach/ Kelly Rohrbach] at [[Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue|SI Swimsuit]]\n\n{{2010\u20132019 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rohrbach, Kelly}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:21st-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Greenwich, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Actresses from New York City]]\n[[Category:American people of German descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Swiss descent]]\n[[Category:American female golfers]]\n[[Category:American female models]]\n[[Category:Georgetown Hoyas women's golfers]]\n[[Category:IMG Models models]]\n[[Category:Actresses of German descent]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American actress and model}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2016}}\n{{Infobox model\n|name = Kelly Rohrbach\n|image = Kelly Rohrbach, 2015.jpg\n|imagesize =\n|caption = Rohrbach in 2015\n| birth_name   = Kelly Rohrbach\n| birth_date   = {{Birth date and age|1990|1|21|mf=yes}}\n| birth_place  = [[New York City, New York]], U.S.\n|nationality = American\n|ethnicity =\n|occupation = Actress, model\n|years_active = 2012\u2013present\n|spouse={{marriage|[[Steuart Walton]]|2019|}}\n}}\n'''Kelly Rohrbach''' (born January 21, 1990) is an American actress and model, best known for her role as [[C. J. Parker]] in the film ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]''.\n\n==Early life and education==\nRohrbach was born in [[New York City]] and raised in [[Greenwich, Connecticut]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/article/kelly-rohrbach-gq-shoot|title=Kelly Rohrbach: 'I don't feel any shyness - it's the California girl in me'|first=Alex|last=Bhattacharji|publisher=}}</ref> She is the daughter of Anne (n\u00e9e Wholly) and Clay Rohrbach, a financier.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/local/region/2015/02/17/Wholey-s-Rohrbach-granddaughter-in-running-for-SI-s-Rookie-of-the-Year-swimsuit-model-Sports-Illustrated/stories/201502170177|title=Wholey's granddaughter in running for SI's swimsuit 'Rookie of the Year'|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/06/why-leonardo-dicaprio-s-new-girlfriend-is-basically-perfect|title=Leonardo DiCaprio's Girlfriend Is Basically Perfect|first=Richard|last=Lawson|publisher=}}</ref> She attended [[Greenwich Academy]]. She played [[golf]] for Greenwich and earned an athletic scholarship to [[Georgetown University]] to play golf for the [[Georgetown Hoyas]]. She graduated from Georgetown in 2012 with a degree in theatre, and enrolled at the [[London Academy of Music and Dramatic Art]] to pursue acting.<ref name=people>{{cite web|author=Sands, Nicole|url=http://www.people.com/article/kelly-rohrbach-5-things-you-need-to-know|title=5 Things You Need to Know About Kelly Rohrbach|work=[[People (magazine)|People]]|date=June 11, 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n[[File:Kelly Rohrbach 2014.jpg|thumb|upright|Rohrbach modeling for Beach Bunny Swimwear in 2014]]\n\nRohrbach had small roles in the TV series ''[[Two and a Half Men]]'', ''[[The New Normal (TV series)|The New Normal]]'', ''[[Rizzoli & Isles]]'', ''[[Broad City]]'', and ''[[Rush (U.S. TV series)|Rush]]''.<ref name=people/>\n\nAfter working in [[Hollywood]] for two years, Rohrbach began modeling.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/models/a10037/kelly-rohrbach-interview-2015/|title=Model Kelly Rohrbach Interview - Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Model Kelly Rohrbach|author=Rutherford, Chrissy|work=[[Harper's Bazaar]]|date=February 20, 2015}}</ref> She appeared in [[Gap Inc.]]'s 2014 holiday marketing campaign<ref name=people/> and for [[Old Navy]] denim in 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/swim-daily/2015/02/24/kelly-rohrbach-old-navy-jeans-commercial|title=Rookie Kelly Rohrbach goes to 'couples therapy' for Old Navy|author=Hendrix, Kelsey|date=February 24, 2015|work=[[Sports Illustrated]]|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref> She appeared in the 2015 ''[[Sports Illustrated]]'' [[Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue|Swimsuit Issue]], and was named its \"Rookie of the Year\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/swim-daily/2015/02/28/kelly-rohrbach-wins-2015-si-swimsuit-rookie-year-award|title=Kelly Rohrbach Wins 2015 SI Swimsuit Rookie of the Year Award|author=Gray, Andy|date=March 1, 2015|work=Sports Illustrated|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref> She played [[C. J. Parker]] in the 2017 feature film ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]'', which is based on the 1989\u20132001 TV series [[Baywatch|of the same name]].<ref>{{cite web|author=Falcone, Dana Rose|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/04/kelly-rohrbach-baywatch-movie|title=Kelly Rohrbach joins cast of Baywatch movie in Pamela Anderson role|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Personal life ==\nRohrbach dated actor [[Leonardo DiCaprio]] in 2015.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/movies/leonardo-dicaprio-and-kelly-rohrbach-split/|title=Leonardo DiCaprio and Girlfriend Kelly Rohrbach Have Split|website=PEOPLE.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-02}}</ref> In 2019, she married attorney and [[Walton family]] heir [[Steuart Walton]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/kelly-rohrbach-walmart-heir-steuart-walton-wedding|title='Baywatch' actress Kelly Rohrbach marries Walmart heir Steuart Walton: report|date=2019-06-14|website=Fox News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-02}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title \n! Role \n! Notes \n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Wilt'' \n| Beatrice \n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''My Last Film'' \n| Ashley \n| Short film \n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Caf\u00e9 Society (2016 film)|Caf\u00e9 Society]]''\n| Woman\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Baywatch (film)|Baywatch]]''\n| [[C. J. Parker]]\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Ocean's 8]]''\n| Herself\n| Cameo\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[A Rainy Day in New York]]''\n| Terry\n| \n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title \n! Role \n! Notes \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[The New Normal (TV series)|The New Normal]]''\n| Amber \n| Episode: \"Dairy Queen\"  \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Two and a Half Men]]''\n| Amber \n| Episode: \"Big Episode: Someone Stole a Spoon\"\n|-\n| 2013\u201314\n| ''[[Rizzoli & Isles]]''\n| Officer Charlotte \"Charlie\" Hansen \n| 2 episodes \n|-\n| 2013\u201315\n| ''The PET Squad Files'' \n| Jayne Duncan \n| 12 episodes \n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Rush (U.S. TV series)|Rush]]''\n| Young hottie \n| Episode: \"Pilot\"\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Love is Relative'' \n| Emily \n| Television film\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Deadbeat (TV series)|Deadbeat]]''\n| Beth \n| Episode: \"The Unholy Trinity\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Broad City]]''\n| Alice Ackerman \n| Episode: \"Philadelphia\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Angie Tribeca]]''\n| Laura Ashley\n| Episode: \"License to Drill\"\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Yellowstone (American TV series)|Yellowstone]]''\n| Cassidy Reid \n| Recurring role; 4 episodes \n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscatinline}}\n* {{IMDb name|4859097}}\n* {{Instagram|kellyrohrbach}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170523165320/http://www.guhoyas.com/sports/w-golf/mtt/rohrbach_kelly00.html Kelly Rohrbach] at guhoyas.com\n* [http://models.com/models/kelly-rohrbach Kelly Rohrbach] at Models.com\n* [https://www.si.com/swimsuit/model/kelly-rohrbac